Key #SoHEU18 findings:
💉 Prevention remains a priority while health accounts for 9.6% of GDP in EU countries.
🏥Unnecessary admissions consume over 37 million hospital bed days each year in the EU.
🚬 Behavioural risk factors account over 790 000 deaths per year in Europe. https://t.co/BXFbc1SSPq
